# ========================================
# TD Realty Ohio - URL Canonicalization
# ========================================

# Canonical URL strategy:
# - HTML pages: Use .html extension (e.g., /sellers.html)
# - Directories: Use trailing slash (e.g., /areas/, /blog/)
# - sitemap.xml: Returns valid XML with HTTP 200

# ----------------------------------------
# Trailing slash redirects for HTML pages
# Redirect /page/ to /page.html
# ----------------------------------------
/sellers/               /sellers.html           301
/buyers/                /buyers.html            301
/contact/               /contact.html           301
/about/                 /about.html             301
/privacy/               /privacy.html           301
/terms/                 /terms.html             301
